Product Description

Wake up Gently with Syslux White Noise Machine Wake Up Light Alarm Clock

  • Wake-Up Light has a unique design like a letter(Q) can be used for special occasion, event, or home decorating.
  • The natural sunrise simulation increased over the span of 60 minutes until it completely wake you up gently.
  • This Sleep Aid digital alarm clock is designed for everyone, especially for heavy sleepers and kids.
  • Sleep-Aid allows at most 120 minutes with 12 soothing sounds to help you fall asleep easily.

Smart Night Light Alarm Clock

LED Display Screen

This Alarm Clock allows you to easily set separate alarms, which can be used to separate weekdays and weekends, or to set different alarms for your family.

Snooze Function

There's an easily-accessible snooze function in case it's still not time to get up, which gives you an extra 9 minutes of sleep; the music plays again after 9 minutes (up to 3 times).

Multi-functional Light

If you're a heavy sleeper, this multi-alarm sunrise alarm clock will ensure you wake up even if the light doesn’t rouse you.

Specification

  • Time format: 12 and 24 Hours
  • USB charging output : 5V , 2A
  • Snooze time: 9 minutes
  • Dimmable: 5%~100% brightness
  • Alarm Sounds: Ringing Sound
  • Sleeping Sounds: 12 Nature sounds and 3 Lullabies

Smart alarm clock provides 15 soothing sounds and you can fall asleep with ease. Ideal for creating a disturbance-free area.

  • Waves - white noise - summer night - thunderstorm - stream - fire charcoal
  • Wind chimes - frog - waterfalls - rain - bird - breeze - baby lullabies

Dimmable Bedside Night Light

Easy to adjust the colorful lights, improve your sleep and boosts your mood. Great bedside night light for kids, Adults and the elderly.

Smart Alarm Clock

Lifetime-free App controls all alarm functions. Setting up sunrise alarm mode to get gently wake up refreshed.

White Noise Rhythm Light

Pick your favorite sound among 15 natural sound options together with soft lights, or connect with your phone Bluetooth to enjoy your own music.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

  • Christaloo
    3.0 out of 5 stars Tiny numbers, unreliable app, USB plug = three strikes against this clock
    Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2025
    Color: WhiteAmazon Vine Customer Review of Free Product( What's this? )
    I bought this for my son when he was 12, thinking it would be a great way for him to start learning to wake himself up. Well, I didn't realize it required an app to use, so he had to wait a couple of months until his 13th birthday when he got a phone to be able to use it. This was over a year ago, and I just realized 1) I never reviewed it and 2) it's been sitting unplugged in a dark corner of his room for who knows how long now after being used for a short while early on.

    I asked him what he thought of the clock and why he wasn't using it. He said the lights were too bright, the alarm sounds were weird and he didn't like any of them, and the app didn't always work. Well, I assume the lights should have been able to be controlled or turned off by the app, but if the app wasn't always working, then that's a problem. As for the alarm sounds, I never heard any of them, but I guess that's a personal preference.

    I thought if he didn't want to use it, I'd try it out, but I'm sitting here with it plugged in right next to me and I can already tell there are a couple obvious reasons I won't like it. First, it only has a USB plug. That's a pain. I don't have a USB outlet in my bedroom, and it would require me to purchase a separate piece just to use a clock? No, thanks. Second, the numbers are TINY and I can barely see the time with my contacts IN! There is no way I'd be able to see this clock without my glasses or contacts in the middle of the night. And personally, I'm not into the lights and sounds features - that was something I thought would appeal to my kid.

    So unfortunately, I'm not sure if this clock will get much use in our house.
